    DynamicProgrammingAlgoImpl
    is a pseudo-polynomial algorithm: It is polynomial time in the value W, which denotes the number of possible weights (if the weights are fractional, we can multiply them by a common factor so that they are all integers.) It works by trading space for time: A large table is used to memoize state for subproblems.
    DynamicProgrammingAlgoImplTest
